org.jlab.mya

Class DataNexus

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jlab.mya.DataNexus
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    OnDemandNexus, PooledNexus

    public abstract class DataNexus
extends Object
    Manages the possibly multiple data sources required to service requests to a cluster of Mya hosts. Two configuration files (Java properties) are required to be in the class path: (1) credentials.properties and (2) deployments.properties. If these files are not found this class will throw an ExceptionInInitializerError upon being loaded by the class loader.
    Author:
    slominskir
